using node 14.17.0
execute: pm2 start (to start) | pm2 stop all (to stop) | pm2 logs (to check logs on console)
log files go to ~/.pm2/logs
at the bottom of the market_maket.js script we can modify to run daily using a cron job or just run once (manually)
Instructions on the file


.env file configs

POLYGON_NETWORK_RPC = https://polygon-mainnet.infura.io/v3/PROJECT_ID
#mainnet https://polygon-mainnet.infura.io/v3/PROJECT_ID
#testnet https://polygon-mumbai.infura.io/v3/PROJECT_ID

